Package: chatlot
Title: Process Lots of Chats
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Process lots of large language model chats with 'ellmer'.
    Provides both sequential and parallel processing of chat interactions
    with features including tool calling and structured data extraction.
    Enables workflow management through progress tracking and recovery. 
    Additional quality-of-life features include verbosity (or echo) control 
    and sound notifications. Parallel processing is implemented using 'future'.
    Includes methods for retrieving progress status, chat texts, and chat objects.
